---
title: Spiced Chicken & Bacon Roast Veggie Toss with Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Who doesn’t like a bit of char on their chicken? This one gets a coating of our famous Aussie-style spice blend before it crisps up in
the pan until golden. Finish it off with a bed of roasted veggies and a sprinkling of bacon bits for an outstanding pairing of flavours.
